			<h3>Vinaora Visitors Counter</h3>
			<p>Version: <b>1.5.3.2</b></p>
			<p>Release date: <b>2009-02-06</b></p>
			<p>Homepage: <b><a href="http://vinaora.com/" title="Joomla! Guides - Hướng dẫn Joomla!" target="_blank">http://vinaora.com/</a></b></p>
			<p>This module shows you the visitors of your site.</p>
			<h4>Features</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>6 cool styles</li>
				<li>Show Today - Yesterday - Week - Month - All statistics</li>
				<li>Custom Pre-text and Post-text</li>
				<li>A script based on mod_digit_counter by http://www.iw1qlh.net/</li>
				<li>Valid <b><u>XHTML</u></b> and <b><u>CSS</u></b></li>
			</ul>
		]]>
